<i>She's shy.</i>

33
00:06:32,088 --> 00:06:35,885
<i>Don't give up, cousin. l think she likes you.
l see a real future there.</i>

34
00:06:36,344 --> 00:06:37,719
Sweet of you to say.

35
00:06:37,784 --> 00:06:41,200
A ring, a church wedding,
all her family would show.

36
00:06:41,273 --> 00:06:44,023
<i>And then for the reception,
you'd kill them all.</i>

37
00:06:44,281 --> 00:06:46,169
<i>l know. lt'd be magical.</i>

38
00:06:47,450 --> 00:06:50,450
<i>You know what we are, Vivian?
We're romantics.</i>

39
00:06:50,522 --> 00:06:52,978
<i>''We'' are nothing.</i>

40
00:06:53,946 --> 00:06:56,184
And the thing about romantics is

41
