Yes, on top is how l imagine you.

44
00:07:06,973 --> 00:07:08,981
That looks fun. Can l be next?

45
00:07:09,054 --> 00:07:11,158
Absinthe all around. Her, too.

46
00:07:11,230 --> 00:07:14,133
<i>Well. Out from their caves,
if it isn't the Fortunate Five.</i>

47
00:07:14,207 --> 00:07:15,155
<i>We're in luck, gents.</i>

48
00:07:15,231 --> 00:07:17,206
My cousin deigns
to honor us with her presence.

49
00:07:17,279 --> 00:07:20,149
-Are you here to dance, Vivian?
-Dance. Yeah. Shake your pretty tail.

50
00:07:20,224 --> 00:07:22,941
<i>l'd like to see how you'll dance for Gabriel.</i>

51
00:07:26,593 --> 00:07:28,732
My cousin, you know you will.

52
00:07:30,210 --> 00:07:33,505
<i>Seven years, it's almost time.</i>

53
00:07:33,761 --> 00:07:36,096
He has other girls to choose from.

54
00:07:37,635 --> 00:07:39,097
None like you.

55
00:07:41,923 --> 00:07:44,771
To darling Vivian. Pride of the pack.

56
00:07:44,835 --> 00:07:47,356
-And her bright future.
-Vivian!

57
00:07:51,174 --> 00:07:52,351
Vivian.

58
00:09:06,418 --> 00:09:07,662
Hello?

59
00:09:09,395 --> 00:09:11,370
ls there somebody in here?

60
00:09:11,795 --> 00:09:14,665
